reviews.text: Local restaurant, not eye catching and most of the food here are just normal. However, the best food in this shop is the rice noodles. You can pick your own preferences and I personally think this is the best food around this area. Many people, even those from local also don't know it. ( Because they didn't promote this ). Highly recommended. If in case someone see my post here and also feel the same, please like my post, so other people would know. 😃
